    "We employ the proposed PSO model, as well as 8 classical search methods and 4 PSO variant algorithms, for hyperparameter search, including PSO, ABC [36], Salp Swarm Algorithm (SSA) [44], SSO [38], Bare-bones PSO (BBPSO) [63], Flower Pollination Algorithm (FPA) [64], FA [32], Dragonfly Algorithm (DA) [65], Genetic PSO (GPSO) [40], PSO with sine coefficients (SPSO) [20], a BBPSO variant with attractiveness and evade actions (BBPSOV) [49] and PSO with adaptive sine, circle and spiral coefficients (ACPSO) [66]."
